ofiber
======

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/ofiber.svg
   :target: https://pypi.org/project/ofiber/

.. image:: https://mybinder.org/badge_logo.svg
   :target: https://mybinder.org/v2/gh/scottprahl/ofiber/master?filepath=docs

